0:03:18.180,0:03:21.060
THE WORK OF FAITH

0:03:21.060,0:03:27.200
Today, we see the work of faith as a risk.

0:03:27.200,0:03:31.820
Christians today see the work of faith as a risk.

0:03:31.820,0:03:36.940
How can I believe what I can’t see with my eyes?

0:03:36.940,0:03:46.320
The work of faith is not a risk but a sure and practical act.

0:03:46.320,0:03:50.200
How can I believe what I do not see?

0:03:50.200,0:04:00.140
We are used to what we see and feel; what you can see by yourself, perceive and feel.

0:04:00.140,0:04:02.620
These are things we are used to.

0:04:02.620,0:04:10.980
But for me now to begin to believe in what I do not see...

0:04:10.980,0:04:13.800
We see it as a risk.

0:04:13.800,0:04:26.700
The work of faith is not a risk but a sure and practical act.

0:04:26.700,0:04:34.960
If a person has not received the teaching of the Scriptures,

0:04:34.960,0:04:38.800
if you have not been grounded in the Word

0:04:38.800,0:04:52.260
or you have not received the promise of the Holy Spirit in your spirit,

0:04:52.260,0:05:01.160
forcing yourself to do such acts is indeed a risk.

0:05:01.160,0:05:05.720
You must be grounded in the Word.

0:05:05.720,0:05:09.940
If you have not been grounded in the Word of God,

0:05:09.940,0:05:20.400
there will be nothing in your heart for the Spirit of God to use or remind you of.

0:05:20.400,0:05:22.520
One would be empty; the heart would be empty.

0:05:22.520,0:05:24.780
Heart means spirit.

0:05:24.780,0:05:29.180
When the heart is empty, there is nothing for the Spirit to use.

0:05:29.180,0:05:34.380
It is not all up to you, certainly, it is not all up to Him;

0:05:34.380,0:05:41.320
your genuineness plus His ability makes it happen.

0:05:41.320,0:05:48.960
If you are empty, there is nothing for Him to use.

0:05:48.960,0:05:53.920
You must be grounded in the Word.

0:05:53.920,0:05:57.160
He uses The Word in our heart.

0:05:57.160,0:06:03.880
This is why we give you the "faith bracelet" to meditate.

0:06:03.880,0:06:12.260
Meditation in the Word of God is a visit with God.

0:06:12.260,0:06:19.000
If a person has not received the teaching of the Scriptures,

0:06:19.000,0:06:24.220
if you have not been grounded in the Word of God

0:06:24.220,0:06:31.820
or you have not received the promise of the Holy Spirit in your heart,

0:06:31.820,0:06:45.320
forcing yourself to do such acts – be healed, be delivered, be saved, in Jesus’ name - is indeed a risk.

0:06:45.320,0:06:50.440
Anything that comes by force is not faith.

0:06:50.440,0:06:56.440
Force...

0:06:56.440,0:06:58.740
Effortless.

0:06:58.740,0:07:13.360
If your work of faith is conscious and pretentious, you have not yet learned the lesson of faith.

0:07:13.360,0:07:19.540
If you have faith in the finished work of our Lord Jesus Christ,

0:07:19.540,0:07:29.560
these acts are spontaneous and unpretentious – natural, without sweat.

0:07:29.560,0:07:34.240
Be healed, be delivered - you are not the one doing this, it is God.

0:07:34.240,0:07:36.700
The work of healing is not our work.

0:07:36.700,0:07:38.880
Healing - it is not our work.

0:07:38.880,0:07:40.140
Deliverance - it is not our work.

0:07:40.140,0:07:41.620
It is God's work.

0:07:41.620,0:07:44.940
When it comes to healing, it is not me.

0:07:44.940,0:07:52.000
