0:07:52.000,0:07:58.340
Giving you money is a way of receiving a blessing because that healing is not my work.

0:07:58.340,0:08:07.780
If I go ahead and give you money to help you, bless you as well, it is a way of receiving a blessing from God.

0:08:07.780,0:08:12.020
I cannot say that I healed; I am not the one who is healing.

0:08:12.020,0:08:18.300
Don't be surprised if a man of God prays for you and heals you, and at the same time gives you money.

0:08:18.300,0:08:22.080
