You give me money after my healing?

0:08:22.080,0:08:25.640
No, don't be surprised because that healing is not his work.

0:08:25.640,0:08:31.620
He is just being used as a "material".

0:08:31.620,0:08:37.180
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:08:37.180,0:08:42.380
Don't be surprised if man of God prays for you and heals you...

0:08:42.380,0:08:46.140
"I am healed" - "You have to pay"

0:08:46.140,0:08:47.680
No!

0:08:47.680,0:08:52.380
