0:09:18.960,0:09:23.540
One might say, "I have faith in that job".

0:09:23.540,0:09:27.080
That is not the kind of faith we are talking about here.

0:09:27.080,0:09:31.680
The kind of faith we are talking about here is a trust.

0:09:31.680,0:09:33.940
Faith means a trust.

0:09:33.940,0:09:36.880
T R U S T

