0:09:38.520,0:09:41.620
Just love everyone; trust only God.

0:09:41.620,0:09:44.100
Don’t trust me, just love me.

0:09:44.100,0:09:47.760
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:09:47.760,0:09:54.260
You can only trust Someone who has no beginning and has no end.

0:09:54.260,0:09:57.700
I have a beginning and an end.

0:09:57.700,0:10:03.540
Only Jesus has no beginning and has no end – trust Him.

0:10:03.540,0:10:10.980
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:10:10.980,0:10:19.120
If you have faith in the finished work of our Lord Jesus Christ, that is "by His stripes"...

0:10:19.120,0:10:27.900
All what we are looking for - blessing, victories, salvation, or whatever - they are all past issues.

0:10:27.900,0:10:38.020
The healing, victory, deliverance - they are past, on the cross.

0:10:38.020,0:11:09.100
All the way to Calvary
He went for me

0:11:09.100,0:11:19.760
He went to set me free

0:11:19.760,0:11:27.120
They are all past events.

0:11:27.120,0:11:34.800
You have no reason to be sick, to suffer.

0:11:34.800,0:11:40.640
In Him there is nothing like that.

0:11:40.640,0:11:50.500
If you have faith in that - that is what I call "finished work"...

0:11:50.500,0:12:19.400
